  "description": "A large container ship is docked at a port, being assisted by a tugboat. The ship is heavily loaded with colorful shipping containers stacked high on its deck. A massive, complex port crane looms over the ship, seemingly in the process of unloading or loading cargo. The hull of the ship is rusty, indicating extensive use. The water around the ship is choppy, showing the wake of the tugboat. In the background, there's a hazy view of land with hills or mountains and some industrial structures. The scene suggests a bustling international trade hub.",
